				<td colspan="2"><span>*quote* Can't i just leave twisting abillities alone? *quote*
<br />
NO<img src="/skins/default/images/emotions/emotion-1.gif" border="0" alt="Smiley" hspace="2" />
<br />

<br />
but on lower lvls twisting is hard cus of missed notes, you can buy some pretty good low priced instruments in katta, like 3 plat or so.
<br />
you can always try to twist with the melody feature, but with so low lvl song skill as at lvl25 i wouldnt recommend it, but here goes how to work it.
<br />
make a hotkey like this, /melody &lt;song1&gt; &lt;song3&gt; &lt;song4&gt;
<br />
depended in what order you want to use the songs in.
<br />
but i recommend at lower lvls you stick to the 11 22 33 44 twisting, its easyer with all the missed notes.
<br />

<br />
chandra
